<span><img alt="No WiFi" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-386579" height="16" src="https://www.airlinequality.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/No_WiFi.png" width="48"/>Onboard WiFi</span><br/>
<span><img alt="power_icon" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-386553" height="16" src="https://www.airlinequality.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/power_icon.png" width="48"/>USB power</span><br/>
<span><img alt="AVOD" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-386555" height="16" src="https://www.airlinequality.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/avod_icon.png" width="48"/>Audio / video on demand</span><br/>
<span><img alt="Dining" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-386556" height="16" src="https://www.airlinequality.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/meals_icontick.png" width="48"/>Complimentary meal</span><br/>
<span><img alt="Wines" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-386557" height="16" src="https://www.airlinequality.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/wines_icon.png" width="48"/>Complimentary beverages &amp; wines</span><br/>
<span><img alt="Sleeping" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-386560" height="16" src="https://www.airlinequality.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/sleeping_icon.png" width="48"/>Pillow / blanket</span></p>
