<div class="customWidget">
<div class="WidgetTitle">
<h2>FIRST CLASS</h2>
</div>
<div class="widgetContent">
<p>British Airways offers First Class on many long haul routes operated by widebody aircraft (Boeing 747-400, Boeing 777, Boeing 787 and the A380). Most aircraft have 14 flat-bed seats in First Class, and 8 seats on the Boeing 787-9.  <br/>
<span></span><br/>
<span><img alt="flat_seats" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-386552" height="16" src="https://www.airlinequality.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/flat_seats.png" width="48"/>Flat bed seat / suite</span><br/>
<span><img alt="power_icon" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-386553" height="16" src="https://www.airlinequality.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/power_icon.png" width="48"/>In-seat &amp;/or USB power</span><br/>
<span><img alt="No WiFi" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-386579" height="16" src="https://www.airlinequality.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/No_WiFi.png" width="48"/>Onboard WiFi</span><br/>
<span><img alt="AVOD" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-386555" height="16" src="https://www.airlinequality.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/avod_icon.png" width="48"/>Audio / video on demand</span><br/>
<span><img alt="Dining" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-386556" height="16" src="https://www.airlinequality.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/meals_icontick.png" width="48"/>On demand dining</span><br/>
<span><img alt="Wines" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-386557" height="16" src="https://www.airlinequality.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/wines_icon.png" width="48"/>Fine wines &amp; beverage service</span><br/>
<span><img alt="Sleeping" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-386560" height="16" src="https://www.airlinequality.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/sleeping_icon.png" width="48"/>Pillows &amp; duvet / blanket</span><br/>
<span><img alt="Pyjamas" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-386561" height="16" src="https://www.airlinequality.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/pjs_icon.png" width="48"/>Pyjamas / Sleepsuit</span><br/>
<span><img alt="Amenities" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-386562" height="16" src="https://www.airlinequality.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/amenity_icon.png" width="48"/>Amenity kit</span></p>
