<div class="WidgetTitle">
<h2>PREMIUM ECONOMY</h2>
</div>
<div class="widgetContent">
<p>British Airways offers a premium economy cabin on their long haul / widebody aircraft, branded as World Traveller Plus. With the exception of the larger seat, the onboard service and product varies little to the standard long haul Economy class. <br/>
